{"tid":854851,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"戴偉浚集體炒車事件","createTime":"2018-10-09T16:00:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T08:23:45.000Z","uid":35846,"like":12,"dislike":277,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"ba2c11605886727f8f3fb1d16a7b695d0071bddd","tid":854851,"uid":35846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T16:00:52.000Z","msg":"<strong><br />\nDai has just recovered from a knee injury while playing for Oxford United&rsquo;s Under-23 and <span style=\"color: red;\">White said he would not be pushing it by including the 19-year-old on the side at this stage.</span><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Dai will not be joining us for these games [friendlies] but we will definitely be keeping a close tab on him in the coming months as we lead up to the East Asia Cup,&rdquo; said White at Yuen Long Stadium on Sunday.</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/sport/football/article/2167378/hong-kong-coach-gary-white-picks-his-final-23-dai-wai-tsun-fails-make\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Farticle%2F2167378%2Fhong-kong-coach-gary-white-picks-his-final-23-dai-wai-tsun-fails-make&d=9muGD2B2HDW9YKzsh4glQf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=93563091\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/sport/football/article/2167378/hong-kong-coach-gary-white-picks-his-final-23-dai-wai-tsun-fails-make</a><br />\n<br />\n唔揀佢個選擇權好似係GW 到，好似唔係Dai 話唔踢<br />\n<br />\n中媒就咁樣出 ：<br />\n韋特解釋：「戴偉浚剛傷愈，今仗尚未有足夠體能應付，但直至東亞錦標賽外圍賽前，我們會繼續密切注意他；而霍斌仁方面，他的球會未能及時為他開綠燈，我真的很想徵召他，但他未能及時在明天報到，我們也會繼續為東亞外而留意他。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2/244199/%E6%B8%AF%E8%B6%B3-%E5%8A%A0%E5%88%A9%E9%9F%8B%E7%89%B9%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83%E4%BB%BB%E5%85%A7%E9%A6%96%E5%BC%B5%E6%B1%BA%E9%81%B8%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE-%E9%83%AD%E5%98%89%E8%AB%BE%E5%85%BC%E4%BB%BB%E6%B8%AF%E9%9A%8A%E5%8A%A9%E6%95%99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%25AB%2